    <title>Wankel Rotary Engine: Epitrochoidal Envelopes</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        #demo-container {
            max-width: 800px;
